-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://it.vtc.edu.hk/pcpd/ModuleDetail.php?ID=52</a>"},{"pid":"0e08104470fc3283f8313035d97a6ef63eee37ce","tid":425930,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:14:28.000Z","msg":"4年應該過30"},{"pid":"ee72be3dccfb0fbb53c4a0f85dc75a12279287d6","tid":425930,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4年應該過30</blockquote><br />\n27、28 姐，當佢23歲入行，如果degree 係part time, 25,26歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8421fa24a2f7427961a7d84813ead22637e3e1c","tid":425930,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4年應該過30</blockquote><br />\n27、28 姐，當佢23歲入行，如果degree 係part time, 25,26歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我指30k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de67f128074aa2811ad9a00a18acb8d46213343","tid":425930,"uid":90442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁4年起碼會咩價先</blockquote><br />\n睇乎能力<br />\n非fg個價其實好難講<br />\n<br />\nios/android programmer 4 yr exp, 大約接近30k掛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好認同，IT 講幾年經驗其實reference 價值好少<br />\n<br />\n4年經驗都可以爭好遠，有能力30K up 絕對唔會少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人認真答真係好少有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n能力係指識咩lang, 做過咩project咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得，能力係指<br />\n1. 你既skill有幾符合佢請人要求<br />\n2. 無人乜都識（乜Q都識就你揀工唔係工揀你啦），唔識照直講<br />\n3. interview 時既自信<br />\n見工時間好短，九成既interviewer 都係睇印象，CV你寫你識9000 樣野都係假，唔知你識得幾深入，請你入黎做返一頭半個月，就實睇到<br />\n<br />\n如果你個賣點係「4年經驗」，咁真係好難揀得落手<br />\n以web development 為例<br />\n有D 